ActFirearms Act
SubjectUnited States Enforcement Officers Exemption Order, 2020 (Transportation of Firearms), No. 2
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2020-170 of March 24, 2020; and (2) making the UNITED STATES ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS EXEMPTION ORDER, 2020 (TRANSPORTATION OF FIREARMS), NO. 2 in order to add the Saint-Zacharie, Quebec location to permit U.S. law enforcement officers to transit through this location until March 31, 2025.
